Les timbres ?

354
00:16:39,698 --> 00:16:41,188
Timbres-point-com.

355
00:16:41,233 --> 00:16:43,497
Trois petits mots
qui m'ont sauvé la vie...

356
00:16:43,535 --> 00:16:45,503
"timbres, point, com".

357
00:16:45,537 --> 00:16:47,903
